<h3>&nbsp;</h3> 
<h3 id="toc3" class="bonfire"><a name="x--Trivia"></a>Trivia</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>The Japanese translates to: "A glass bottle of dull green. A treasure of the Undead. / Accumulate estus at a bonfire and drink to restore HP. / Since ancient times, journeys of the Undead have&nbsp;been around bonfires. The Estus bottle was always part of the journey."</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
